data.description: This home qualifies for 100 percent financing! The seller is willing to offer an updating allowance with an acceptable offer. This home can also qualify for a down payment grant! This is a HUGE HOME!! 4 BEDROOMS 2 FULL BATHS AND 2 PARTIAL BATHS! THIS HOME HAS TWO STORIES AND LOTS OF SPACE. IT HAS AN OPEN FLOOR PLAN, PLENTY OF STORAGE SPACE, AN OFFICE, FIREPLACE, AND A BALCONY OVERLOOKING THE BEAUTIFUL, FENCED IN YARD! THE NICE CARPORT IS A NICE WAY TO KEEP YOUR CAR PROTECTED FROM THE ELEMENTS. THIS ONE IS ONE FOR THE BOOKS! COME SCHEDULE YOUR PRIVATE TOUR! THIS ONE WILL NOT LAST LONG! THIS IS GREAT DEAL FOR THE AREA! MOTIVATED SELLER CONSIDERING ALL OFFERS! THE HOME IS SOLD AS IS.
